## ðŸš€ Quick Start

```bash
# Clone and build
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/terminal-time-machine
cd terminal-time-machine
cargo build --release

# Record your terminal session
cargo run --bin record
# (Do your work in the terminal...)
# Press Ctrl+C when done recording

# Replay the session
cargo run --bin play
